TITLE: Implementing Responsive Grid Layout with VirtuosoGrid Components (TSX)
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to configure `VirtuosoGrid` using the `components` prop to provide custom `List` and `Item` components. The custom components are styled with flexbox to create a responsive grid layout. It also shows how to wrap and style the content of each virtualized grid item.
SOURCE: https://github.com/petyosi/react-virtuoso/blob/master/apps/virtuoso.dev/docs/guides/virtuoso-grid/grid-responsive-columns.md#_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: tsx
